{"tid":1165742,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"辛尼特都入到下季歐聯第一種子","createTime":"2019-05-22T04:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:08:13.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"33e91cac457a83587445e79bf110c445fba671ed","tid":1165742,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"下季歐聯小組賽，皇馬、馬體會都將成為二檔球隊參加抽籤，這意味他們將遇到一檔種子隊。一檔種子隊是各大聯賽的冠軍，具備不俗的實力。<br />\n<br />\n  目前已經敲定一檔種子隊的球隊有巴塞、曼城、祖記、拜仁、巴黎聖日耳門、辛尼特。另外兩個名額屬於歐聯冠軍跟歐霸盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n  歐聯冠軍將在利物浦跟熱刺之間產生，而歐霸盃冠軍將在車路士跟阿仙奴之間誕生。（亞瑟"},{"pid":"8886dbaee3c657e66d3c22e75f254d127007ae69","tid":1165742,"uid":69568,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"下年3隊英超pot 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365bd1f1d98f748eceae4e44c185b04582e6717f","tid":1165742,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8886dbaee3c657e66d3c22e75f254d127007ae69","tid":1165742,"uid":69568,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"下年3隊英超pot 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"歐霸都1好"},{"pid":"e624ef0ca100f9e8e0791683bf18be84de810b52","tid":1165742,"uid":2216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"點解俄超冠軍都係pot 1?"},{"pid":"d865d005b973f1c38834f27d5967f32b9ede03c8","tid":1165742,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365bd1f1d98f748eceae4e44c185b04582e6717f","tid":1165742,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8886dbaee3c657e66d3c22e75f254d127007ae69","tid":1165742,"uid":69568,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"下年3隊英超pot 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"歐霸都1好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05